sql:
SELECT SUM(pctl_2_5) AS total_2_5th_percentile
FROM air_quality_measurements
WHERE measurement_id IN (SELECT measurement_id FROM weather_conditions);

external_knowledge:
PM2.5 refers to particulate matter that is 2.5 micrometers or less in diameter; 
Kings County, NY, is a county in New York City;
The date '2020-04-09' refers to April 9th, 2020.
